k gold in the 200m butterfly earlier this evening, defeating Hungary's world and Olympic record holder Kristof Malik.\", \"from\": 1385, \"to\": 1524, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1468, \"end\": 1475, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8802304839457636, \"rank\": 0.13606608523418728, \"text\": \"Hungary\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1518, \"end\": 1523, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maalik\", \"score\": 0.9983795804408939, \"rank\": 0.0016226554680453223, \"text\": \"Malik\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maalik\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maalik\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then he rocked up once again for the 200m breaststroke, blitzing the competition tobecome the first competitor to win two swimming golds in one night since 1976.\", \"from\": 1526, \"to\": 1687, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Not even swimming's greatest-ever, Michael Phelps, has matched Marchand's achievement tonight, sending his compatriots into a frenzy.\", \"from\": 1689, \"to\": 1822, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1724, \"end\": 1738, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.175445337124025e-88, \"text\": \"Michael Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\"}, {\"begin\": 1752, \"end\": 1760, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.703246578269033e-18, \"text\": \"Marchand\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q11774891\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brad_Marchand\"