pedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Felix Dolci was involved in scary scenes when his handguard split in two when he was preparing to dismount,causing him to fall from the bars onto the mat.\", \"from\": 5093, \"to\": 5247, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5093, \"end\": 5098, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Felix_Mendelssohn\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.243180356149198e-14, \"text\": \"Felix\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Felix_Mendelssohn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Felix_Mendelssohn\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The arena let out a huge gasp as the Canadian struggled to get to his feet, holding his bloodied hand.\", \"from\": 5249, \"to\": 5351, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5286, \"end\": 5294, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"score\": 0.9999999920974005, \"rank\": 7.90231770144565e-09, \"text\": \"Canadian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dolci got to his feet and discussed the prospect of returning to the competition, doing so a few moments later with a sore hand - but fell again in another sore landing.\", \"from\": 5353, \"to\": 5522, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He then took the bars again to finish, scoring 11.733 to huge applause as those in Paris recognised the incredible mental toughness needed to carry on.\", \"from\": 5524, \"to\": 5675, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5607, \"end\": 5612, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.158478594575822e-30, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Australian Jesse Moore then suffered a second fall of the competition, landing awkwardly on his neck, but was able to return to action.\", \"from\": 5677, \"to\": 5812, \"entiti